text: This isn't about me picking sides, I want both DC and Marvel to succeed, BUT if I you honestly believe this trailer is any different from the ones given to the THIRTEEN other Marvel films, you are kidding yourselves. DC had amazing trailers for Wonder Woman and Suicide Squad. Justice League was not a trailer it was a collection of footage shown, it was not meant to be viewed as a first trailer. I'm not saying Doctor Strange trailer was bad, but it was nothing new. DC gave us something new to be excited for. If you can't see that, then I'm sorry, you don't have to be excited, but don't talk smack when you don't have a leg to stand on. Yes DC has dissapointed lately, that doesn't make the trailers look any less good at doing their job.
